message.title: Volt info We've scheduled in some maintenance
message.summary: Between Thu 8 Jul 4:00am-7:00am AEST, the app and card will be unavailable
message.description: Between Thursday 8 July 4:00am - 7:00am AEST, the app will be down while we make our updates. This also includes certain card features, which means you won't be able to activate your card, set your PIN, make purchases, or withdraw or check your balance at ATMs. Once maintenance is complete, you'll be able to use all features as normal.
